==Chinese==
===Mandarin===
[[Pinyin]]: shībài shì chénggōng zhī mŭ
===Proverb===
'''[[失敗]][[是]][[成功]][[之]][[母]]'''
# Failure is the mother of success.
===Alternate forms===
[[失败是成功之母]] ([[Simplified Chinese]])

